s do not reproduce well are likely\naffected by deviations from LTE, but we conclude that our understanding of UV\natmospheric opacities is fairly complete for early A-type stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2005 13:58:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-16"}
