ottom-up\" approach, M-theory is taken as a\nmotivating background.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2005 20:51:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Apr 2005 20:33:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-05"}
